{"title":"鼓浪屿琴声","authors":["黄秉荣"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪屿琴声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄秉荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪屿听不见车轮辘辘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听到悦耳的琴声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安静吗？好静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却又引动海内外人们谛听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴声，从窗口飘出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过石砌的墙头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日光岩上萦绕三匝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落入大海，溅起碧波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤知音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴声是沟通海峡的春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤来信鸽传带心语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为相思树上绚丽的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家披绿，户户琴音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚琴者从无名到有名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榕树的每条根须都是琴键"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个小岛就是一架神州之琴"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}